title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your objective eye allows you to see multiple sides of a problem. Naturally, you want to help lift the fog for all involved, but your idealistic impulses might encounter a snag if you misread the situation. Youre not looking for a fight, but you could inadvertently create one today. You prefer to collaborate on endeavors that foster cooperation and justice. Nevertheless, be careful about jumping to an incorrect conclusion and overreacting before you consider the consequences of your actions. Author Ralph Waldo Emerson wrote, Peace cannot be achieved through violence, it can only be attained through understanding. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
